### Login Passenger

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
"email": "dev@test.com",
"password": "StrongPassword123!"
}

###

### Login Driver

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
"email": "driver@test.com",
"password": "StrongPassword123!"
}

###

### Create Ride

POST {{baseUrl}}/rides
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
"pickupLat":30.0668,
"pickupLng":79.0193,
"destLat":30.3165,
"destLng":78.0322,
"pickupAddress":"IIT Roorkee",
"destAddress":"Haridwar"
}

###

### Get My Rides

GET {{baseUrl}}/rides
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}

###

### Get Active Ride

GET {{baseUrl}}/rides/active
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}

###

### Get Ride By Id

GET {{baseUrl}}/rides/{{rideId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}

###

### Cancel Ride

POST {{baseUrl}}/rides/{{rideId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
"reasonCode":"PASSENGER_CHANGED_MIND"
}

###

### Cancel Again (422)

POST {{baseUrl}}/rides/{{rideId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
"reasonCode":"PASSENGER_CHANGED_MIND"
}

###

### Driver Read Ride (Phase 3A → 403)

GET {{baseUrl}}/rides/{{rideId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{driverToken}}

###

### Driver Create Ride (403)

POST {{baseUrl}}/rides
Authorization: Bearer {{driverToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
"pickupLat":30.0668,
"pickupLng":79.0193,
"destLat":30.3165,
"destLng":78.0322
}
